@startuml
title Viaverse Review / Trust / Badge / Gamification — Activity Diagram
start
:JobCompleted;
:Create two-sided review prompts;
:User submits review\nrating + tags + comment;
:Validate eligibility\njob participant + one review;
if (Valid?) then (yes)
  :Moderation scan\nabuse / PII / hate / spam;
  if (Safe to publish?) then (yes)
    :Publish review;
  else (no)
    :Queue for admin review;
    :Admin approves or rejects;
  endif
  :Recalculate trust score;
  :Evaluate badge rules;
  :Award/revoke badges;
  :Update points/streaks;
  :Update ranking/search signal;
  :Emit trust events;
else (no)
  :Reject duplicate / invalid;
endif
stop

note bottom
Trust/ranking updates must be resistant to abuse:
one review per side per job, duplicate prevention,
suspicious review detection and admin moderation.
end note
@enduml
